---
title: Mexican Chicken Tortilla Bake with Sour Cream
description: Here's a recipe for success: Tex-Mex chicken, melted cheddar and sour cream, all coming together in perfect harmony.  It’s bubbling and oozy, with soft tortilla soaked in sauce below and crispy edges up top – how could it not impress?
